name: Cherry Bishop
description: The best way to describe myself is to give you a sneak peak into my space… When you walk in my front door your right smack in my livingroom. I have the usuals…couch, chairs, tv, radio. At any point you will find a Flatts cd in my radio thats my life. I am 27 year’s old, single never married , I`m 5’8 with a athletic build, mentally stable, physically fit, a bunch of laughs, warm, caring, honest, good listening, God Fearing, and a positive person.I am real easy person to talk to and a good listener.I love to play golf and I enjoy chilling with my friend/family, I like watching movies, swiming, fishing, playing video games, listening to music dancing, going out on dates, traveling, going bowling.I am a family oriented person and I get along with everyone in my family and outside my family.
